classes that should be equivalent to the Server library. It also utilizes a 
specific loader template. We should think about if we want to support both 
approaches (pre-shrunk library vs. generator-based class selection), and if 
yes, if we need another skeleton that uses the pre-shrunk library. In any case, 
the relation of the skeletons to the Server component should be made clear, 
prob. also reflected in the skeletons&#39; names.</thetext>
